Package fr.inria.lille.shexjava.schema.parsing

Class ShExJParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.lille.shexjava.schema.parsing.ShExJParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parser
    public class ShExJParser
extends Object
implements Parser
    Parses a ShexSchema from its jsonld representation. This implementation does not support: external definitions, semantic actions and anonymous "start" shapes.
    Author:
    Iovka Boneva, Jérémie Dusart
